  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育系统的数据流图。核心是学生数据库，我把它叫做StudentDB。然后还要有一个LMS门户，老师学生登录用的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，StudentDB和LMS门户。那GradeSync这个成绩同步服务需要出现吗？它应该是独立节点还是和LMS合并？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "GradeSync要独立出来，而且我得强调——它有两个实例：一个是核心同步服务，另一个是备份节点。所以图上会有两个GradeSync节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "两个GradeSync节点，一个主一个备。那ContentCDN内容分发网络呢？视频课件那些。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，ContentCDN要有。另外我需要几个中间处理节点：一个叫Place，一个叫Signal，还有一个Risk。它们负责数据清洗和风险评估。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Signal",
        "Risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把所有节点都加上了。现在画关系：StudentDB指向主GradeSync，LMS门户和GradeSync之间是双向的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "双向对，LMS和GradeSync互相调用。还有ContentCDN指向备份GradeSync，然后主GradeSync也连到备份GradeSync。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "记下了。那中间节点呢？Place、Signal、Risk怎么连？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Signal",
        "Risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Risk指向Signal，Signal指向备份GradeSync。Place单独指向Press——Press是个输出节点，打印成绩报告用的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Press这个节点你之前没提过，我现在补上去。Place→Press，Risk→Signal，Signal→Barg，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Press",
        "Place",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Press是报表输出。再检查一下：ContentCDN→Define（备份GradeSync），Audit→Define（StudentDB到主GradeSync），都没问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Audit",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部画好了。我数一下：Audit、Bail、Barg、Code、Define五个业务节点，加上Place、Press、Signal、Risk四个处理节点，共九个节点。关系也都连上了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Signal",
        "Risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美。这个图能清楚展示数据从学生库出发，经过CDN和同步服务，最后风险审核和报表输出的完整链路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
